CustomField.description: The time interval between each vertical line. Examples: 00:05 = 5 minutes, 24:00 = one day, 7.00:00 = one week.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: L’intervalle de temps entre chaque ligne verticale. Exemples : 00:05 = 5 minutes, 24 h = un jour, 7.00:00 = une semaine.
CustomField.label: Slot Duration
